    <values>
        <field>Remediation_Steps__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Identify all Salesforce integrations that transmit or store cardholder data and map the data flow. Use Salesforce connected apps with IP restrictions to limit API access to authorized network segments only. Configure login IP ranges on profiles that access payment-related objects. Validate segmentation effectiveness through penetration testing at least annually.</value>
